@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lajogv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((v0 / wp.exp(v1 + 0.38)) / v0)
    tmp = v0
    v2 = (wp.sin(v0) * wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.27)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.cos((tmp + 0.14 + tmp + 0.96)))
    v2 = tmp
    v0 = v2
    v2 = (wp.cos(0.81) / ((v0 + 0.31 + tmp + 0.71) - v0))
    data[tid] = v0
